uno.collections.lists

Interface List<E>

  • Type Parameters:
    E - The type of an individual element to be stored in the list.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ArrayList, LinkedList

    public interface List<E>
    This interface specifies the behaviors of an abstract data type for list collections. A list is an indexed, linear collection of like type elements, supporting dynamic insertion and removal at any valid index.
